---
// CTA section with gradient background
---

<section class="py-20 px-6">
  <div
    class="max-w-5xl mx-auto rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden relative text-center py-24 px-6"
  >
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518837695005-2083093ee35b?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop"
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
      alt="Agua"
    />

    <!-- Gradient Overlay -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/80 to-cyan-600/80 backdrop-blur-[2px]"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="relative z-10 text-white">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">
        Solicita Una Cotización Gratuita
      </h2>
      <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Descubre lo fácil que puede ser tener agua purificada ilimitada.
        Contáctanos por WhatsApp y te respondemos al instante.
      </p>

      <!-- WhatsApp Button -->
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/5219991336108?text=Hola,%20me%20gustaría%20solicitar%20una%20cotización%20para%20el%20sistema%20Purifreze"
        target="_blank"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full font-bold text-lg transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-2xl hover:shadow-green-500/50"
      >
        <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp text-3xl"></i>
        Solicitar Cotización por WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
